Author: bir_die
Text: Sometimes when I’m a vindictive shitbaby I definitely do it for attention. That’s when I’m super over dramatic and hoping I pass out in front of whomever I’m pissed at because, you know, that’s a logical and reasonable way to communicate.   Otherwise I’m pretty private about it because it’s a pretty personal thing for me (outside of here). I’m more obsessive over numbers than my body.
